answerText: Desdemona[10] Desdemona's handmaid is this wife of the villain Iago; she steals the handkerchief Iago uses to make Othello think Desdemona has been unfaithful.

question: Question:  [10] Name this daughter of Brabantio, accused of adultery and eventually murdered by her Moorish husband Othello.
